headline: Paychex Declares Quarterly Dividend
summary: ROCHESTER, N.Y., January 10, 2025--The Board of Directors of Paychex, Inc. declared a regular quarterly cash dividend on Paychex common stock of $0.98 per share payable on February 27, 2025 to shareholders of record as of February 7, 2025.
